"{\"uid\": \"newsweek.com-luana-alonso-speaks-out-removed-olympics-village-paris-1935006\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  Aug 06, 2024 at 02:48 AM EDT  updated  Aug 06, 2024 at 03:52 PM EDT  Entertainment Editor  Swimmer Luana Alonso has broken her silence on claims she was asked to leave the Olympic Village after creating an \\\"inappropriate atmosphere.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.7436572851554526, \"rank\": 0.23076923076925165, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8314086914097976e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paraguayan athlete took toInstagramon Monday to \\\"clarify\\\" what had happened, amid reports as to her reason for leaving Paris.\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9988948139692101, \"rank\": 0.0011064052683691776, \"text\": \"Paraguayan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999986033659046, \"rank\": 1.396636113969478e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old had previously failed to qualify in the 100-meters butterfly in the heat last week.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside a picture of a sunset, Alonso hit out at the \\\"lies\\\" in view of her 643,000 followers.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She wrote in Spanish: \\\"I just wanted to clarify that I was never kicked out or expelled from anywhere, please stop spreading false information.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to make any statement but I am not going to let lies affect me either.\\\"\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paraguay's Olympic chief Larissa Schaerer previously released a statement to various publications which read: \\\"Her presence is creating an inappropriate atmosphere within Team Paraguay.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9987937642182736, \"rank\": 0.0012076920889922084, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larissa Schaerer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\"}, {\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9987937642182736, \"rank\": 0.0012076920889922084, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We thank her for proceeding as instructed, as it was of her own free will that she did not spend the night in the athletes' village.\\\"\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes can decide whether to stay in the Village, which accommodates more than 14,000 competitors.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No further information was given on what the alleged behavior was, with Alonso seemingly then returning to the U.S.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The star, who is studying at Southern Methodist University in Dallas, Texas, shared a video which saw her approaching border control.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Methodist_University\", \"score\": 0.9997486035708627, \"rank\": 0.0002449052270045345, \"text\": \"Southern Methodist University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Methodist_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Methodist_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\", \"score\": 0.9998367573046699, \"rank\": 0.00013218268617443504, \"text\": \"Dallas\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.5724207271992063, \"rank\": 0.7108672219398297, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso narrowly missed on the semi-finals after placing sixth, just 0.24 seconds behind Georgia's Ana Nizharadze.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.7877663509437147, \"rank\": 0.23292430844131096, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\"}, {\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nizharadze\", \"score\": 0.99999835337575, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nizharadze\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nizharadze\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nizharadze\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Luana Alonso (@luanalonsom)  On July 28, she sensationally announced her retirement from the sport, writing on the picture sharing app: \\\"Swimming: thank you for allowing me to dream, you taught me to fight, to try, perseverance, sacrifice, discipline and many more.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.8124999943797706, \"rank\": 0.23076923076925165, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gave you part of my life and I do not change it for anything in the world because I lived the best experiences of my life, you gave me thousands of joys, friends from other countries that I will always carry them in my heart, unique opportunities.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not goodbye, it's see you soon.\\\"\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Amid speculation her retirement was due to her performance in France, she confirmed otherwise in an interview credited to Claro Sports.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9642809784565216, \"rank\": 0.034602015975832276, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"People, my decision was made a long time ago.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't because of the Games \\u2026 I just have to thank everyone who always supported me.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It did not happen the way I wanted it to.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I sincerely apologize to Paraguay, but I did what I could, despite several things that happened to me before.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2527, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9987937642182736, \"rank\": 0.0012076920889922084, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I am happy and also to retire here with a full stadium and finally have the Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso made her Olympic debut age 17 at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025Newsweek Digital LLC\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}]}"